---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | Keita Eriawan"
  description="About Keita Eriawan and this personal website."
  pageTheme="about"
>
  <section class="page-shell" aria-labelledby="about-title">
    <div class="page-grid">
      <aside class="page-label">
        <span>03</span>
        <strong id="about-title">About</strong>
        <span>Personal context</span>
      </aside>

      <div class="about-layout">
        <article class="about-panel">
          <h1>Part data practice, part public notebook.</h1>
          <p>
            This space will hold the human context: what I do, what I am learning,
            the kind of work I want to be known for, and the questions I keep returning to.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="about-panel">
          <div class="meta">
            <span>Contact</span>
            <span>Open</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            A compact contact block keeps the site focused while leaving room to add links,
            social profiles, and a more personal biography later.
          </p>
          <a class="contact-pill" href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email me</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
